<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-52-0220 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper represents a review of Section 522 of the new Federal SurfaceMining Act. Its primary purposes are to attempt an understanding of thenew legislation and to offer some suggestions on implementation. It proceedsfrom general concepts to specific points in an effort to locate areasof conflicting ideas. Specific suggestions are offered for state implementationand shows actual information to be collected.</TEXT></DOC>